{
  "stem": "13251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I think maybe one-- one of those kids I know, mother survived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But most of them, I don't think-- they were probably in the same position we were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, I was watching a video last night, which I hadn't seen in a few years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I went to the 50th year reunion, and the stories that people were telling were-- were so much like mine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like-- it was that-- they were told when-- because they came with-- with children transports, like I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were told that the parents were supposed to follow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the war broke out, and it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they ended up in-- in concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was the last they heard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's exactly what happened to my parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that was probably pretty much common what was-- what-- what happened to most--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, a little bit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, we were in Ely for-- till the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were probably one of the last people that went back to London.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because most of the kids who had-- because in Ely, we-- we were not refugees, we were evacuees.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, can I check that page, please?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
